{
  "info": {
    "name": "BPM Primes API",
    "description": "Collection pour tester l'API BPM Primes Blueline\n\n## Authentification\n1. Signup → crée un compte (message + user, pas de token)\n2. Login → récupère un JWT (stocké automatiquement dans variable `token`)\n3. Toutes les autres requêtes utilisent `{{token}}`\n\n## Dates\n- Format: YYYY-MM-DD (start_date / end_date)\n- Anti-chevauchement: pas de même type de prime sur période qui se chevauche\n\n## Workflow validation\nCréer prime → Valider N+1 → Valider Directeur → Valider DG → Clôture auto\n(Impossible de sauter une étape)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8000" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "token_n1", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Signup (Inscription)",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "exec": ["console.log(pm.response.json().message || 'Inscription effectuée'); console.log('Utilise Login pour récupérer un token')"],
              "type": "text/javascript"
            }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/signup",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"nouveau@blueline.mg\",\n  \"name\": \"Nouvel Utilisateur\",\n  \"password\": \"monPassword123\",\n  \"poste\": \"Développeur\",\n  \"department\": \"DSI\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Connexion)",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "exec": ["var jsonData = pm.response.json(); if (jsonData.access_token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', jsonData.access_token); console.log('Token stocké !'); }"],
              "type": "text/javascript"
            }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"nouveau@blueline.mg\",\n  \"password\": \"monPassword123\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Mon profil (me)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/me",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login DG",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "exec": ["var jsonData = pm.response.json(); if (jsonData.access_token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', jsonData.access_token); console.log('Token DG stocké !'); }"],
              "type": "text/javascript"
            }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"dg@blueline.mg\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login N+1 (Manager)",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "exec": ["var jsonData = pm.response.json(); if (jsonData.access_token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token_n1', jsonData.access_token); console.log('Token N+1 stocké !'); }"],
              "type": "text/javascript"
            }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"vonjy.rakotoniaina@staff.blueline.mg\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login DRH",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "exec": ["var jsonData = pm.response.json(); if (jsonData.access_token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', jsonData.access_token); console.log('Token DRH stocké !'); }"],
              "type": "text/javascript"
            }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"johary.drh@blueline.mg\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Directeur",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "exec": ["var jsonData = pm.response.json(); if (jsonData.access_token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', jsonData.access_token); console.log('Token Directeur stocké !'); }"],
              "type": "text/javascript"
            }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"rivo@gulfsat.mg\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
